        <span>
          <span class="text-default dark:text-white">Reliability</span>
          <span class="font-medium text-muted dark:text-slate-400"> through </span>
          <span class="text-default dark:text-white">Simplicity</span>
        </span>
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="subtitle">
        <span class="hidden sm:inline">
          <span class="font-semibold">Top Grade Tech</span> helps you prevent downtime, thwart attacks, and protect revenue with managed IT, cybersecurity, and communications built for continuity.</span
        >
        <span class="block mb-1 sm:hidden font-bold text-blue-600">Top Grade Tech: Reliability Through Simplicity.</span>
        Trusted by businesses across the US for proactive support, cyber defense, and communications systems that keep operations moving without interruption.
      </Fragment>
